## Project Overview

GigLens is an Android app for DoorDash gig drivers that analyzes delivery offers via screenshot sharing.

### User Flow:
Driver shares a DoorDash screenshot to GigLens

App uses ML Kit OCR to extract offer data (pay, restaurant, distance, times)

StreetExtractor parses pickup/dropoff street names from OCR text

GeocodingHelper estimates road distances using GPS or manual region

OfferScorer calculates net value = pay - (vehicle cost + time cost)

Result displayed as floating pill widget + optional full-screen overlay

Widget persists on screen, draggable, expandable to mini/full details

Toggle in Settings enables/disables the widget

