Scoring Formula (IMPLEMENTED)
Variables
text
pickup_miles    = Driver → restaurant (deadhead miles from OCR)
delivery_miles  = Time-based estimate (capped at 15mi)
total_miles     = pickup_miles + delivery_miles
Time Calculation
text
drive_to_pickup_min = (pickup_miles / 45mph) × 60
prep_time_min       = 2 min (configurable)
delivery_drive_min  = Time remaining after pickup + prep (capped)
minutes_on_job      = drive_to_pickup + prep_time + delivery_drive
Cost Calculation
text
vehicle_cost    = total_miles × cost_per_mile     (default $0.90/mile)
time_cost       = minutes_on_job / 60 × hourly_rate (default $15/hr)
total_cost      = vehicle_cost + time_cost
net_value       = pay_amount - total_cost
Verdict Thresholds
text
TAKE       = Score >= 65
BORDERLINE = Score >= 40
SKIP       = Score < 40
